<headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 14 at 7:39AM EDT  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...AREAS OF FOG EARLY THIS MORNING...
Some fog has developed across the area. The fog is locally dense,
reducing visibility to one quarter mile or less in places.
Motorists should be prepared for changing visibility along their
route during the morning commute. The fog will decrease after 9
am allowing visibility to improve.</description>
